summary: When I was a kid, if there had been an artist I adored (even half as much as I do Taylor) who created a song and video like this...
body:
When I was a kid, if there had been an artist I adored (even half as much as I do Taylor) who created a song and video like this — one filled with so much self-love and pride in what makes you different (like a rainbow with all of the colors) — I doubt that I would’ve spent as long as I did, consumed with shame and guilt over my identity, hidden away in the closet.

Think of the positive impact she’s having.
